aced,plural=agentruntimes\n// +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n    Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n#### 3.2 CodeInterpreter (`codeinterpreter_types.go`)\n- **File**: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`\n- **GVK**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1, Kind=CodeInterpreter`\n- **Resource plural**: `codeinterpreters`\n- **Types**: `CodeInterpreter`, `CodeInterpreterSpec`, `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`, `CodeInterpreterStatus`, `CodeInterpreterList`\n- **Key pattern**: `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` uses **flat fields** (not embedded PodSpec)\n- **Unique fields**: `WarmPoolSize *int32`, `AuthMode AuthModeType`, `Ready bool` in status\n\n#### 3.3 Shared Types (in `codeinterpreter_types.go`)\n- `ProtocolType` (enum: `HTTP`, `HTTPS`)\n- `AuthModeType` (enum: `picod`, `none`)\n- `TargetPort` struct (`PathPrefix`, `Name`, `Port`, `Protocol`)\n\n---\n\n### 4. Typical CRD Structure/Pattern in This Project\n\nEvery CRD follows this consistent pattern:\n\n| Component | Pattern |\n|-----------|---------|\n| **Root struct** | Embeds `metav1.TypeMeta` + `metav1.ObjectMeta`; has `Spec` and `Status` fields |\n| **Kubebuilder markers** | `+genclient`, `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`, `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`, `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`, `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"...` |\n| **List struct** | Embeds `metav1.TypeMeta` + `metav1.ListMeta`; has `Items []<CRDType>`; markers: `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...`, `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` |\n| **Scheme registration** | `func init() { SchemeBuilder.Register(&<Type>{}, &<Type>List{}) }` |\n| **Kind constants** | Defined in `register.go`: `<Type>Kind`, `<Type>ListKind`, `<Type>GroupVersionKind` |\n| **JSON tags** | camelCase, with `omitempty` on optional fields |\n| **Pointer fields** | Optional fields use pointers (`*metav1.Duration`, `*int32`, `*string`) |\n| **Status** | Always includes `Conditions []metav1.Condition`; may have convenience bools like `Ready` |\n\n**Infrastructure files** (shared across all CRDs in the package):\n- `doc.go`: `// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` + `// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- `groupversion_info.go`: `GroupVersion`, `SchemeBuilder`, `AddToScheme`\n- `register.go`: Kind constants, `SchemeGroupVersion` alias, `Resource()` helper\n- `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`: Auto-generated by `controller-gen object`\n\n---\n\n### 5. CodeInterpreter-Related Code Found\n\n**Existing implementation files:**\n\n| File | Path | Description |\n|------|------|-------------|\n| Types definition | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | Full CRD types (82 lines) |\n| Types tests | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types_test.go` | Unit tests (158 lines) |\n| DeepCopy (generated) | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | DeepCopy for all CodeInterpreter types |\n| Kind constants | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | `CodeInterpreterKind`, `CodeInterpreterGroupKind`, etc. |\n\n**Documentation files:**\n\n| File | Path | Description |\n|------|------|-------------|\n| Proposal | `changes/AR-002/proposal.md` | AR-002 proposal (128 lines) |\n| Design | `changes/AR-002/design.md` | Detailed design spec (669 lines) |\n| Tasks | `changes/AR-002/tasks.md` | Task list (mostly placeholder, 10 lines) |\n| Delta spec | `changes/AR-002/delta-spec.md` | Delta specification |\n| SDD prompt | `.sdd_prompt.md` | Prompt for generating design.md |\n\n**client-go generated code** (referenced in `deployment/client-go.md`):\n- `CodeInterpreterInterface` - typed REST client\n- `CodeInterpreterInformer` / `CodeInterpreterLister`\n- `FakeCodeInterpreter` - test double\n\n---\n\n### 6. AR-002 and ST-3 Documentation\n\n**AR-002** (`changes/AR-002/`):\n- **Title**: \"CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\"\n- **Stage**: ST-0 (Scaffold)\n- **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n- **Status**: The `tasks.md` is a placeholder -- it says \"待补充：具体任务分解（依赖 proposal 和 design 完成后填充）\" (to be filled after proposal and design are complete)\n- The `proposal.md` and `design.md` are fully written and detailed\n\n**ST-3**: No references to \"ST-3\" or \"ST-03\" were found anywhere in the project. The stages referenced are:\n- AR-001: Stage ST-4 (Implementation)\n- AR-002: Stage ST-0 (Scaffold)\n\n---\n\n### Summary of Key Differences: AgentRuntime vs CodeInterpreter\n\n| Dimension | AgentRuntime | CodeInterpreter |\n|-----------|-------------|-----------------|\n| Sandbox template | `SandboxTemplate` embeds `corev1.PodSpec` | `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` uses flat fields |\n| Warm pool | None | `WarmPoolSize *int32` |\n| Auth mode | None | `AuthMode AuthModeType` (picod/none) |\n| Status | Only `Conditions` | `Conditions` + `Ready bool` |\n| Ports JSON tag | `targetPort` | `ports` |\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_2897d12feffeGsMJVVAYuZ26jK","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775809785087,"end":1775809883972}}}}
