{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775809888068,"sessionID":"ses_2897d33c5ffeqQ82qCou8llhnY","part":{"id":"prt_d76847a500017Hg8plp2ljCTY6","messageID":"msg_d76846f8b001iQpoMKvjIsfK8V","sessionID":"ses_2897d33c5ffeqQ82qCou8llhnY","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_acad11dbba1343ca8d2e4f03","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002 任务清单\n2: \n3: > **Stage**: ST-0 (Scaffold)\n4: > **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n5: > **Language**: Go\n6: > **Size**: S\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: > 待补充：具体任务分解（依赖 proposal 和 design 完成后填充）\n\n(End of file - total 10 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002 任务清单\n\n> **Stage**: ST-0 (Scaffold)\n> **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n> **Language**: Go\n> **Size**: S\n\n---\n\n> 待补充：具体任务分解（依赖 proposal 和 design 完成后填充）","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775809888059,"end":1775809888066}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775809889302,"sessionID":"ses_2897d33c5ffeqQ82qCou8llhnY","part":{"id":"prt_d76847ff80015X0QmTITtbvy2i","messageID":"msg_d76846f8b001iQpoMKvjIsfK8V","sessionID":"ses_2897d33c5ffeqQ82qCou8llhnY","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_d4d93167af2a47bd897c6b67","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 — 设计说明\n2: \n3: ## 1. 架构\n4: \n5: ### 1.1 定位\n6: \n7: `CodeInterpreter` 是 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统的 Custom Resource Definition (CRD)，与 `AgentRuntime` 共享同一 API Group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。它声明式地定义代码解释器沙箱的运行环境模板，是 CodeInterpreter 控制器、client-go 生成代码、CLI/SDK 的类型基础。\n8: \n9: 与 `AgentRuntime` 的差异：\n10: - `AgentRuntime` 使用通用 `SandboxTemplate`（直接嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`），面向通用 AI Agent 沙箱\n11: - `CodeInterpreter` 使用专用 `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`，提供更细粒度的字段（`Image`、`Command`、`Args`、`Resources`、`RuntimeClassName` 等），面向代码解释器场景\n12: - `CodeInterpreter` 独有 `WarmPoolSize`（预热池大小）和 `AuthMode`（认证模式）字段\n13: - `CodeInterpreterStatus` 额外包含 `Ready` 布尔字段\n14: \n15: ### 1.2 包结构\n16: \n17: CodeInterpreter 类型定义与 AR-001 共享 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 包：\n18: \n19: ```\n20: pkg/apis/\n21: └── runtime/\n22:     └── v1alpha1/\n23:         ├── doc.go                      # 包文档 + k8s 代码生成标记\n24:         ├── groupversion_info.go        # GroupVersion + SchemeBuilder (controller-runtime 风格)\n25:         ├── register.go                 # Kind 元数据 + Resource 辅助函数\n26:         ├── codeinterpreter_types.go    # CodeInterpreter CRD + 共享类型（本变更核心）\n27:         ├── codeinterpreter_types_test.go # CodeInterpreter 类型测试\n28:         ├── agent_type.go               # AgentRuntime CRD 类型定义 (AR-001)\n29:         └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go    # controller-gen object 自动生成\n30: ```\n31: \n32: ### 1.3 依赖关系\n33: \n34: ```\n35: CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n36:   ├── k8s.io/api/core/v1          (corev1.PodSpec, PullPolicy, EnvVar, ResourceRequirements)\n37:   ├── k8s.io/apimachinery         (metav1.TypeMeta, ObjectMeta, Duration, Condition)\n38:   ├── sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime (scheme.Builder)\n39:   │\n40:   ├──→ make generate              产出 zz_generated.deepcopy.go\n41:   ├──→ make gen-crd               产出 manifests/charts/base/crds/*.yaml\n42:   ├──→ make gen-client            产出 client-go/ (Typed Client, Informer, Lister, Fake)\n43:   └──→ CodeInterpreter Controller 通过 Informer/Lister 消费 CodeInterpreter 资源\n44: ```\n45: \n46: ### 1.4 代码生成工具链\n47: \n48: | 工具 | 版本 | 用途 |\n49: |------|------|------|\n50: | controller-gen | v0.17.2 | DeepCopy 方法生成 + CRD YAML 生成 |\n51: | k8s.io/code-generator | v0.34.1 | client-go 代码生成 (Typed Client, Informer, Lister, Fake) |\n52: \n53: 生成入口：`make gen-all` → `generate` + `gen-client`。\n54: \n55: ---\n56: \n57: ## 2. 数据结构\n58: \n59: ### 2.1 包声明与代码生成标记 (`doc.go`)\n60: \n61: ```go\n62: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package\n63: // +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n64: package v1alpha1\n65: ```\n66: \n67: ### 2.2 GroupVersion 与 Scheme (`groupversion_info.go`)\n68: \n69: ```go\n70: package v1alpha1\n71: \n72: import (\n73:     \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n74:     \"sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme\"\n75: )\n76: \n77: var (\n78:     GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}\n79:     SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n80:     AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n81: )\n82: ```\n83: \n84: ### 2.3 Kind 元数据 (`register.go`)\n85: \n86: ```go\n87: var (\n88:     CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n89:     CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n90:     CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n91:     CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n92: \n93:     AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n94:     AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n95:     AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n96: )\n97: \n98: var SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n99: \n100: func Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n101:     return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n102: }\n103: ```\n104: \n105: ### 2.4 共享类型 (`codeinterpreter_types.go`)\n106: \n107: 以下类型被 `AgentRuntime` 和 `CodeInterpreter` 共同使用：\n108: \n109: ```go\n110: // ProtocolType 定义端口协议\n111: type ProtocolType string\n112: \n113: const (\n114:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n115:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n116: )\n117: \n118: // AuthModeType 定义认证模式\n119: type AuthModeType string\n120: \n121: const (\n122:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n123:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n124: )\n125: \n126: // TargetPort 定义沙箱暴露的端口\n127: type TargetPort struct {\n128:     PathPrefix string       `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n129:     Name       string       `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n130:     Port       uint32       `json:\"port\"`\n131:     Protocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n132: }\n133: ```\n134: \n135: ### 2.5 CodeInterpreter 核心类型 (`codeinterpreter_types.go`)\n136: \n137: #### 2.5.1 CodeInterpreter (CR 根类型)\n138: \n139: ```go\n140: // +genclient\n141: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n142: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n143: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n144: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n145: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n146: \n147: type CodeInterpreter struct {\n148:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n149:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n150: \n151:     Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n152:     Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n153: }\n154: ```\n155: \n156: **Kubebuilder 标记说明：**\n157: \n158: | 标记 | 作用 |\n159: |------|------|\n160: | `+genclient` | 为 client-go 代码生成器标识此类型需要生成 Typed Client |\n161: | `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...` | DeepCopy 方法实现 runtime.Object 接口 |\n162: | `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` | 标记为 kubebuilder object root，生成 DeepCopyObject |\n163: | `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` | 启用 `/status` 子资源，分离 spec/status 更新权限 |\n164: | `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced` | 命名空间级资源（REST 复数形式由代码生成器自动推导为 `codeinterpreters`） |\n165: | `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"...` | `kubectl get codeinterpreters` 输出中显示 Age 列 |\n166: \n167: #### 2.5.2 CodeInterpreterSpec\n168: \n169: ```go\n170: type CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n171:     Ports              []TargetPort                    `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n172:     Template           *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n173:     SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration                `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n174:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration                `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n175:     WarmPoolSize       *int32                          `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n176:     AuthMode           AuthModeType                    `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n177: }\n178: ```\n179: \n180: **字段语义：**\n181: \n182: | 字段 | 类型 | 必填 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n183: |------|------|------|--------|------|\n184: | `ports` | `[]TargetPort` | 否 | `[]` | 沙箱暴露的端口配置，为空时控制器不配置路由端口 |\n185: | `template` | `*CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` | 是 | — | 沙箱模板，定义容器镜像、命令、资源等 |\n186: | `sessionTimeout` | `*metav1.Duration` | 否 | `15m` | 空闲超时后沙箱被清理 |\n187: | `maxSessionDuration` | `*metav1.Duration` | 否 | `8h` | 沙箱从创建到强制销毁的最大时长 |\n188: | `warmPoolSize` | `*int32` | 否 | `0` | 预热池大小，控制器维持的空闲沙箱数量 |\n189: | `authMode` | `AuthModeType` | 否 | `\"\"` (空) | 认证模式：`picod` 或 `none` |\n190: \n191: #### 2.5.3 CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate\n192: \n193: ```go\n194: type CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n195:     Labels           map[string]string             `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n196:     Annotations      map[string]string             `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n197:     RuntimeClassName *string                       `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n198:     Image            string                        `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n199:     ImagePullPolicy  corev1.PullPolicy             `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n200:     ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n201:     Environment      []corev1.EnvVar               `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n202:     Command          []string                      `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n203:     Args             []string                      `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n204:     Resources        corev1.ResourceRequirements   `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n205: }\n206: ```\n207: \n208: **字段语义：**\n209: \n210: | 字段 | 类型 | 必填 | 默认值 | 说明 |\n211: |------|------|------|--------|------|\n212: | `labels` | `map[string]string` | 否 | `{}` | 注入到沙箱 Pod 的额外标签 |\n213: | `annotations` | `map[string]string` | 否 | `{}` | 注入到沙箱 Pod 的额外注解 |\n214: | `runtimeClassName` | `*string` | 否 | `nil` | 运行时类名称（如 `kuasar-vmm`），用于指定沙箱运行时 |\n215: | `image` | `string` | 否 | `\"\"` | 容器镜像 |\n216: | `imagePullPolicy` | `corev1.PullPolicy` | 否 | `\"\"` | 镜像拉取策略 |\n217: | `imagePullSecrets` | `[]corev1.LocalObjectReference` | 否 | `[]` | 镜像拉取密钥引用 |\n218: | `environment` | `[]corev1.EnvVar` | 否 | `[]` | 容器环境变量 |\n219: | `command` | `[]string` | 否 | `[]` | 容器入口命令 |\n220: | `args` | `[]string` | 否 | `[]` | 容器入口参数 |\n221: | `resources` | `corev1.ResourceRequirements` | 否 | `{}` | 容器资源请求和限制 |\n222: \n223: **设计决策：** `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` 使用扁平字段而非嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`。\n224: \n225: | 方案 | 优点 | 缺点 |\n226: |------|------|------|\n227: | 扁平字段（已选） | CRD YAML 精简；字段语义明确；适合代码解释器场景 | 需手动映射到 PodSpec；不支持 PodSpec 全部能力 |\n228: | 嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`（AgentRuntime 方案） | 完整 Kubernetes 能力；无需维护字段映射 | CRD YAML 较大（~1000 行）；对代码解释器场景字段过多 |\n229: \n230: 选择扁平字段的原因：CodeInterpreter 是面向代码解释器的专用 CRD，不需要完整的 PodSpec 能力（如多容器、InitContainer、Volumes 等）。扁平字段使 CRD 更精简、API 更清晰。\n231: \n232: #### 2.5.4 CodeInterpreterStatus\n233: \n234: ```go\n235: type CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n236:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n237:     Ready      bool               `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n238: }\n239: ```\n240: \n241: **字段语义：**\n242: \n243: | 字段 | 类型 | 说明 |\n244: |------|------|------|\n245: | `conditions` | `[]metav1.Condition` | 资源状态条件列表 |\n246: | `ready` | `bool` | 快捷就绪标志，控制器根据 conditions 聚合计算 |\n247: \n248: **预期 Condition 类型（由 CodeInterpreter 控制器写入）：**\n249: \n250: | Type | Status | Reason | 说明 |\n251: |------|--------|--------|------|\n252: | `Ready` | `True` | `SandboxRunning` | 沙箱已成功创建并运行 |\n253: | `Ready` | `False` | `SandboxFailed` | 沙箱创建失败或异常终止 |\n254: | `Ready` | `Unknown` | `Pending` | 沙箱正在创建中 |\n255: \n256: #### 2.5.5 CodeInterpreterList\n257: \n258: ```go\n259: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n260: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n261: \n262: type CodeInterpreterList struct {\n263:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n264:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n265:     Items           []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n266: }\n267: ```\n268: \n269: ### 2.6 数据结构关系图\n270: \n271: ```\n272: CodeInterpreter\n273: ├── TypeMeta (apiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1, kind: CodeInterpreter)\n274: ├── ObjectMeta (name, namespace, labels, annotations, uid, creationTimestamp, ...)\n275: ├── Spec: CodeInterpreterSpec\n276: │   ├── ports: []TargetPort\n277: │   │   ├── pathPrefix: string (optional)\n278: │   │   ├── name: string (optional)\n279: │   │   ├── port: uint32 (required)\n280: │   │   └── protocol: ProtocolType (enum: HTTP|HTTPS)\n281: │   ├── template: *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate (required)\n282: │   │   ├── labels: map[string]string (optional)\n283: │   │   ├── annotations: map[string]string (optional)\n284: │   │   ├── runtimeClassName: *string (optional)\n285: │   │   ├── image: string (optional)\n286: │   │   ├── imagePullPolicy: corev1.PullPolicy (optional)\n287: │   │   ├── imagePullSecrets: []corev1.LocalObjectReference (optional)\n288: │   │   ├── environment: []corev1.EnvVar (optional)\n289: │   │   ├── command: []string (optional)\n290: │   │   ├── args: []string (optional)\n291: │   │   └── resources: corev1.ResourceRequirements (optional)\n292: │   ├── sessionTimeout: *metav1.Duration (default: \"15m\")\n293: │   ├── maxSessionDuration: *metav1.Duration (default: \"8h\")\n294: │   ├── warmPoolSize: *int32 (default: 0)\n295: │   └── authMode: AuthModeType (enum: picod|none)\n296: └── Status: CodeInterpreterStatus\n297:     ├── conditions: []metav1.Condition (optional)\n298:     │   └── {type, status, reason, message, lastTransitionTime, observedGeneration}\n299:     └── ready: bool (optional)\n300: ```\n301: \n302: ---\n303: \n304: ## 3. API 契约\n305: \n306: ### 3.1 GroupVersionKind (GVK)\n307: \n308: | 组件 | 值 |\n309: |------|-----|\n310: | API Group | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n311: | Version | `v1alpha1` |\n312: | Kind | `CodeInterpreter` |\n313: | ListKind | `CodeInterpreterList` |\n314: \n315: ### 3.2 GroupVersionResource (GVR)\n316: \n317: | 组件 | 值 |\n318: |------|-----|\n319: | Group | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` |\n320: | Version | `v1alpha1` |\n321: | Resource | `codeinterpreters` |\n322: | Scope | Namespaced |\n323: \n324: ### 3.3 REST API 端点\n325: \n326: Kubernetes API Server 自动暴露以下端点：\n327: \n328: | Method | Path | 说明 |\n329: |--------|------|------|\n330: | `POST` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters` | 创建 CodeInterpreter |\n331: | `GET` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters/{name}` | 获取单个 CodeInterpreter |\n332: | `GET` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters` | 列出命名空间下的 CodeInterpreter |\n333: | `GET` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/codeinterpreters` | 列出所有命名空间的 CodeInterpreter |\n334: | `PUT` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters/{name}` | 更新 CodeInterpreter (spec) |\n335: | `PATCH` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters/{name}` | 补丁更新 |\n336: | `DELETE` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters/{name}` | 删除 CodeInterpreter |\n337: | `PUT` | `/apis/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1/namespaces/{namespace}/codeinterpreters/{name}/status` | 更新 status 子资源 |\n338: \n339: ### 3.4 示例 YAML\n340: \n341: ```yaml\n342: apiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n343: kind: CodeInterpreter\n344: metadata:\n345:   name: python-interpreter\n346:   namespace: default\n347: spec:\n348:   ports:\n349:     - name: web\n350:       port: 8080\n351:       protocol: HTTP\n352:       pathPrefix: /\n353:   template:\n354:     labels:\n355:       app: code-interpreter\n356:     annotations:\n357:       agentcube.io/runtime: python-3.11\n358:     runtimeClassName: kuasar-vmm\n359:     image: python:3.11-slim\n360:     imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent\n361:     command:\n362:       - python\n363:       - \"-m\"\n364:       - http.server\n365:     args:\n366:       - \"8080\"\n367:     resources:\n368:       requests:\n369:         cpu: \"100m\"\n370:         memory: \"128Mi\"\n371:       limits:\n372:         cpu: \"1\"\n373:         memory: \"512Mi\"\n374:   sessionTimeout: \"15m\"\n375:   maxSessionDuration: \"8h\"\n376:   warmPoolSize: 3\n377:   authMode: picod\n378: ```\n379: \n380: ### 3.5 Scheme 注册\n381: \n382: CodeInterpreter 类型通过 `SchemeBuilder` 注册到 `runtime.Scheme`：\n383: \n384: ```go\n385: func init() {\n386:     SchemeBuilder.Register(&CodeInterpreter{}, &CodeInterpreterList{})\n387: }\n388: ```\n389: \n390: 下游组件（CodeInterpreter Controller、client-go fake client）通过调用 `v1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme)` 将类型注册到自身 scheme。\n391: \n392: ### 3.6 生成的 client-go 接口\n393: \n394: `make gen-client` 基于本类型定义生成以下接口（详见 `deployment/client-go.md`）：\n395: \n396: | 接口 | 方法 | 说明 |\n397: |------|------|------|\n398: | `CodeInterpreterInterface` | `Create`, `Update`, `UpdateStatus`, `Delete`, `Get`, `List`, `Watch`, `Patch` | Typed REST 客户端 |\n399: | `CodeInterpreterInformer` | `Informer()`, `Lister()` | 共享 Informer + Lister |\n400: | `CodeInterpreterLister` | `List(selector)`, `CodeInterpreters(namespace)` | 只读缓存索引 |\n401: | `CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister` | `List(selector)`, `Get(name)` | 命名空间级只读索引 |\n402: | `FakeCodeInterpreter` | 同上 | 内存测试双端 |\n403: \n404: ---\n405: \n406: ## 4. 错误处理\n407: \n408: ### 4.1 验证错误\n409: \n410: Kubernetes API Server 在资源创建/更新时自动执行 kubebuilder 标记定义的验证：\n411: \n412: | 场景 | 验证标记 | 预期错误 |\n413: |------|----------|----------|\n414: | `template` 缺失 | 隐式 (Go 零值检查) | 控制器层拦截，返回应用层错误 |\n415: | `protocol` 非法值 | 无显式 Enum 标记（由应用层校验） | 控制器层拦截 |\n416: | `authMode` 非法值 | 无显式 Enum 标记（由应用层校验） | 控制器层拦截 |\n417: | `sessionTimeout` 格式错误 | 隐式 (metav1.Duration 解析) | `422 Unprocessable Entity`: 解析失败 |\n418: | `warmPoolSize` 负值 | 无显式 Minimum 标记 | 控制器层拦截 |\n419: \n420: ### 4.2 应用层错误\n421: \n422: CodeInterpreter 控制器应定义以下错误类型：\n423: \n424: | 错误 | 触发场景 | HTTP 状态码 |\n425: |------|----------|-------------|\n426: | `ErrCodeInterpreterNotFound` | 查找不存在的 CodeInterpreter | 404 |\n427: | `ErrTemplateMissing` | CodeInterpreter 的 `template` 为 nil | 400 |\n428: | `ErrInvalidAuthMode` | `authMode` 不是 `picod` 或 `none` | 400 |\n429: | `ErrInvalidWarmPoolSize` | `warmPoolSize` 为负值 | 400 |\n430: | `ErrInvalidPort` | `ports` 中端口号为 0 或超出范围 | 400 |\n431: \n432: ### 4.3 默认值处理\n433: \n434: | 字段 | 默认值 | 应用时机 |\n435: |------|--------|----------|\n436: | `sessionTimeout` | `15m` | 控制器在 reconcile 时注入（或 CRD default） |\n437: | `maxSessionDuration` | `8h` | 同上 |\n438: | `warmPoolSize` | `0` | Go 零值（nil 指针视为 0） |\n439: | `authMode` | `\"\"` (空) | Go 零值，控制器根据场景选择默认认证模式 |\n440: | `ports` | `[]` (空切片) | Go 零值，无需注入 |\n441: | `template.imagePullPolicy` | `\"\"` (空) | Go 零值，Kubernetes 默认 `IfNotPresent` |\n442: \n443: ### 4.4 并发安全\n444: \n445: 本包定义的类型本身无状态，不涉及并发。类型实例的并发安全由使用者（Informer cache、CodeInterpreter Controller）保证：\n446: \n447: - Informer 缓存通过 `cache.SharedIndexInformer` 的 RWMutex 保证读写安全\n448: - DeepCopy 方法确保跨 goroutine 传递时进行值拷贝\n449: \n450: ---\n451: \n452: ## 5. 测试策略\n453: \n454: ### 5.1 单元测试\n455: \n456: #### 5.1.1 常量测试\n457: \n458: ```go\n459: func TestProtocolTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n460:     assert.Equal(t, ProtocolType(\"HTTP\"), ProtocolTypeHTTP)\n461:     assert.Equal(t, ProtocolType(\"HTTPS\"), ProtocolTypeHTTPS)\n462: }\n463: \n464: func TestAuthModeTypeConstants(t *testing.T) {\n465:     assert.Equal(t, AuthModeType(\"picod\"), AuthModePicoD)\n466:     assert.Equal(t, AuthModeType(\"none\"), AuthModeNone)\n467: }\n468: ```\n469: \n470: #### 5.1.2 TargetPort 默认值测试\n471: \n472: ```go\n473: func TestTargetPortDefaults(t *testing.T) {\n474:     tp := TargetPort{Port: 8080}\n475: \n476:     assert.Equal(t, uint32(8080), tp.Port)\n477:     assert.Empty(t, tp.PathPrefix)\n478:     assert.Empty(t, tp.Name)\n479:     assert.Equal(t, ProtocolType(\"\"), tp.Protocol)\n480: }\n481: ```\n482: \n483: #### 5.1.3 CodeInterpreterSpec 默认值测试\n484: \n485: ```go\n486: func TestCodeInterpreterSpecDefaults(t *testing.T) {\n487:     ci := &CodeInterpreterSpec{\n488:         Template: &CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate{},\n489:     }\n490: \n491:     assert.Empty(t, ci.Ports)\n492:     assert.Nil(t, ci.SessionTimeout)\n493:     assert.Nil(t, ci.MaxSessionDuration)\n494:     assert.Nil(t, ci.WarmPoolSize)\n495:     assert.Equal(t, AuthModeType(\"\"), ci.AuthMode)\n496: }\n497: ```\n498: \n499: #### 5.1.4 DeepCopy 隔离测试\n500: \n501: ```go\n502: func TestCodeInterpreterSandboxTemplateDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n503:     runtimeClass := \"kuasar-vmm\"\n504:     original := &CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate{\n505:         Labels:           map[string]string{\"app\": \"test\"},\n506:         Annotations:      map[string]string{\"key\": \"value\"},\n507:         RuntimeClassName: &runtimeClass,\n508:         Image:            \"python:3.11\",\n509:         ImagePullPolicy:  corev1.PullIfNotPresent,\n510:         Command:          []string{\"python\", \"-m\", \"http.server\"},\n511:         Args:             []string{\"8080\"},\n512:     }\n513: \n514:     cp := original.DeepCopy()\n515: \n516:     assert.Equal(t, original.Image, cp.Image)\n517:     assert.Equal(t, original.Labels[\"app\"], cp.Labels[\"app\"])\n518:     assert.Equal(t, *original.RuntimeClassName, *cp.RuntimeClassName)\n519: \n520:     cp.Labels[\"app\"] = \"modified\"\n521:     assert.Equal(t, \"test\", original.Labels[\"app\"])\n522: \n523:     cp.Image = \"modified:latest\"\n524:     assert.Equal(t, \"python:3.11\", original.Image)\n525: }\n526: \n527: func TestCodeInterpreterDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n528:     original := &CodeInterpreter{\n529:         ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"test-ci\", Namespace: \"default\"},\n530:         Spec: CodeInterpreterSpec{\n531:             Ports: []TargetPort{{Name: \"web\", Port: 8080, Protocol: ProtocolTypeHTTP}},\n532:             Template: &CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate{\n533:                 Labels: map[string]string{\"app\": \"test\"},\n534:                 Image:  \"python:3.11\",\n535:             },\n536:             SessionTimeout:     &metav1.Duration{Duration: 15 * time.Minute},\n537:             MaxSessionDuration: &metav1.Duration{Duration: 8 * time.Hour},\n538:             WarmPoolSize:       ptrInt32(3),\n539:             AuthMode:           AuthModePicoD,\n540:         },\n541:         Status: CodeInterpreterStatus{Ready: true},\n542:     }\n543: \n544:     cp := original.DeepCopy()\n545: \n546:     assert.Equal(t, original.Name, cp.Name)\n547:     assert.Equal(t, original.Spec.WarmPoolSize, cp.Spec.WarmPoolSize)\n548:     assert.Equal(t, original.Spec.AuthMode, cp.Spec.AuthMode)\n549:     assert.Equal(t, original.Status.Ready, cp.Status.Ready)\n550: \n551:     cp.Spec.WarmPoolSize = ptrInt32(5)\n552:     assert.Equal(t, int32(3), *original.Spec.WarmPoolSize)\n553: }\n554: \n555: func TestCodeInterpreterListDeepCopy(t *testing.T) {\n556:     original := &CodeInterpreterList{\n557:         ListMeta: metav1.ListMeta{ResourceVersion: \"5678\"},\n558:         Items: []CodeInterpreter{\n559:             {ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{Name: \"ci1\", Namespace: \"default\"}},\n560:         },\n561:     }\n562: \n563:     cp := original.DeepCopy()\n564: \n565:     assert.Equal(t, original.ListMeta.ResourceVersion, cp.ListMeta.ResourceVersion)\n566:     assert.Equal(t, len(original.Items), len(cp.Items))\n567:     assert.Equal(t, original.Items[0].Name, cp.Items[0].Name)\n568: \n569:     cp.Items[0].Name = \"modified\"\n570:     assert.Equal(t, \"ci1\", original.Items[0].Name)\n571: }\n572: ```\n573: \n574: #### 5.1.5 Scheme 注册测试\n575: \n576: ```go\n577: func TestCodeInterpreterSchemeRegistration(t *testing.T) {\n578:     scheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n579:     err := v1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme)\n580:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n581: \n582:     gvk := v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n583:     obj, err := scheme.New(gvk)\n584:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n585:     assert.IsType(t, &v1alpha1.CodeInterpreter{}, obj)\n586: \n587:     gvkList := v1alpha1.SchemeGroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreterList\")\n588:     objList, err := scheme.New(gvkList)\n589:     assert.NoError(t, err)\n590:     assert.IsType(t, &v1alpha1.CodeInterpreterList{}, objList)\n591: }\n592: ```\n593: \n594: ### 5.2 测试文件布局\n595: \n596: ```\n597: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n598: ├── codeinterpreter_types.go         # CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n599: ├── codeinterpreter_types_test.go    # CodeInterpreter 类型测试\n600: ├── agent_type.go                    # AgentRuntime 类型定义 (AR-001)\n601: ├── agent_type_test.go               # AgentRuntime 类型测试 (AR-001)\n602: ├── groupversion_info.go             # GroupVersion + SchemeBuilder\n603: ├── groupversion_info_test.go        # Scheme 注册测试\n604: ├── register.go                      # Kind 元数据\n605: ├── register_test.go                 # GVK/GVR 常量测试\n606: └── zz_generated.deepcopy.go         # 自动生成\n607: ```\n608: \n609: ### 5.3 测试运行\n610: \n611: ```bash\n612: # 运行 pkg/apis 下所有测试\n613: go test ./pkg/apis/... -v\n614: \n615: # 运行带覆盖率\n616: go test ./pkg/apis/... -coverprofile=coverage.out\n617: go tool cover -html=coverage.out\n618: ```\n619: \n620: ### 5.4 TDD 关联\n621: \n622: 本变更与 TDD 规范的关联用例：\n623: \n624: | TDD 用例 | 关联 | 说明 |\n625: |----------|------|------|\n626: | TestCase-CI-001 | 直接 | CodeInterpreter 类型是沙箱创建接口的输入基础 |\n627: | TestCase-CI-002 | 直接 | WarmPool 预热逻辑依赖 `warmPoolSize` 字段 |\n628: | TestCase-CI-003 | 直接 | 认证模式路由依赖 `authMode` 字段 |\n629: \n630: ---\n631: \n632: ## 6. 实现步骤\n633: \n634: ### 6.1 文件创建顺序\n635: \n636: 1. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` — CodeInterpreter 核心类型 + 共享类型\n637: 2. `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types_test.go` — 类型测试\n638: 3. 运行 `make generate` — 更新 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n639: 4. 运行 `make gen-client` — 生成 client-go 代码（Typed Client, Informer, Lister, Fake）\n640: \n641: ### 6.2 验证检查清单\n642: \n643: - [ ] `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n644: - [ ] `make generate` 成功更新 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`\n645: - [ ] `git diff --exit-code` 通过（生成文件无意外变更）\n646: - [ ] `CodeInterpreter` GVK = `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1, Kind=CodeInterpreter`\n647: - [ ] GVR resource = `codeinterpreters`\n648: - [ ] `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` 使用扁平字段而非嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`\n649: - [ ] `WarmPoolSize` 字段类型为 `*int32`\n650: - [ ] `AuthMode` 字段类型为 `AuthModeType`\n651: - [ ] `CodeInterpreterStatus` 包含 `Ready` 布尔字段\n652: - [ ] `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` 已添加\n653: - [ ] `+kubebuilder:printcolumn` Age 列已添加\n654: - [ ] `go test ./pkg/apis/...` 全部通过\n655: \n656: ---\n657: \n658: ## 7. 后续变更\n659: \n660: 本变更完成后，以下变更可并行开展：\n661: \n662: | 变更 | 依赖关系 | 说明 |\n663: |------|----------|------|\n664: | CRD YAML 生成 | 依赖 AR-002 | `make gen-crd` 从 kubebuilder 标记产出 CodeInterpreter CRD YAML |\n665: | client-go 生成 | 依赖 AR-002 | `make gen-client` 产出 CodeInterpreter Typed Client/Informer/Lister/Fake |\n666: | CodeInterpreter Controller | 依赖 client-go 生成 | 通过 Informer/Lister 消费 CodeInterpreter 资源，管理沙箱生命周期 |\n667: | WarmPool 预热控制器 | 依赖 AR-002 | 根据 `warmPoolSize` 维持空闲沙箱池 |\n668: | 认证路由 | 依赖 AR-002 | 根据 `authMode` 配置沙箱认证方式 |\n669: | CLI/SDK CodeInterpreter 命令 | 依赖 AR-002 | 提供 `codeinterpreter create/get/list/delete` 命令 |\n\n(End of file - total 669 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义 — 设计说明\n\n## 1. 架构\n\n### 1.1 定位\n\n`CodeInterpreter` 是 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统的 Custom Resource Definition (CRD)，与 `AgentRuntime` 共享同一 API Group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。它声明式地定义代码解释器沙箱的运行环境模板，是 CodeInterpreter 控制器、client-go 生成代码、CLI/SDK 的类型基础。\n\n与 `AgentRuntime` 的差异：\n- `AgentRuntime` 使用通用 `SandboxTemplate`（直接嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`），面向通用 AI Agent 沙箱\n- `CodeInterpreter` 使用专用 `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`，提供更细粒度的字段（`Image`、`Command`、`Args`、`Resources`、`RuntimeClassName` 等），面向代码解释器场景\n- `CodeInterpreter` 独有 `WarmPoolSize`（预热池大小）和 `AuthMode`（认证模式）字段\n- `CodeInterpreterStatus` 额外包含 `Ready` 布尔字段\n\n### 1.2 包结构\n\nCodeInterpreter 类型定义与 AR-001 共享 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 包：\n\n```\npkg/apis/","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/design.md","time":{"start":1775809889292,"end":1775809889299}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775809890549,"sessionID":"ses_2897d33c5ffeqQ82qCou8llhnY","part":{"id":"prt_d7684849b001iQfaITOoYnuzHy","messageID":"msg_d76846f8b001iQpoMKvjIsfK8V","sessionID":"ses_2897d33c5ffeqQ82qCou8llhnY","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_9193e2abb1ac4eafb18fe51c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n2: \n3: ## 概述\n4: 为 CodeInterpreter Custom Resource Definition 创建 Go 类型定义，与 AR-001 共享 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 包中的公共类型（`TargetPort`、`ProtocolType`）。\n5: \n6: ## 元信息\n7: - **Module**: pkg/apis\n8: - **Language**: Go\n9: - **Size**: S\n10: \n11: ## 目的\n12: CodeInterpreter CRD 是 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统中用于声明式管理代码执行沙箱的自定义资源。与 AgentRuntime（面向通用 AI Agent 沙箱）不同，CodeInterpreter 专注于代码解释器场景，提供了更细粒度的沙箱模板控制（镜像、命令、参数、资源等扁平化字段）、预热池大小配置（`WarmPoolSize`）和认证模式（`AuthMode`：`picod` 或 `none`）。本变更将在已有的 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 包中创建完整的 Go 类型定义，为 client-go 代码生成、控制器实现和 CLI/SDK 提供类型基础。\n13: \n14: ## 范围\n15: \n16: ### 包含\n17: 1. **类型定义** — `CodeInterpreter`、`CodeInterpreterSpec`、`CodeInterpreterStatus`、`CodeInterpreterList`\n18: 2. **嵌套类型** — `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`（扁平化沙箱配置，不嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`）、`AuthModeType` 枚举\n19: 3. **共享类型复用** — `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType`（与 AR-001 AgentRuntime 共用）\n20: 4. **Kubebuilder 标记** — `+genclient`、`+kubebuilder:subresource:status`、`+kubebuilder:printcolumn`、`+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`\n21: 5. **Scheme 注册** — 在 `register.go` 中注册 `CodeInterpreter` 和 `CodeInterpreterList` 的 Kind/GVK 常量\n22: 6. **DeepCopy 生成** — `zz_generated.deepcopy.go`（通过 `controller-gen object` 生成）\n23: \n24: ### 不包含\n25: - CRD YAML 文件生成（由 `make gen-crd` 在 `make generate` 中产出）\n26: - client-go 客户端代码生成（由 `make gen-client` 产出，依赖本变更的类型定义）\n27: - Controller/Reconciler 实现（后续变更）\n28: - WarmPool 控制器逻辑（后续变更）\n29: \n30: ## 类型定义概要\n31: \n32: ```\n33: CodeInterpreter (namespaced CRD)\n34: ├── Spec: CodeInterpreterSpec\n35: │   ├── ports: []TargetPort (optional) — 与 AgentRuntime 共享\n36: │   │   ├── pathPrefix: string (optional)\n37: │   │   ├── name: string (optional)\n38: │   │   ├── port: uint32 (required)\n39: │   │   └── protocol: ProtocolType (enum: HTTP|HTTPS)\n40: │   ├── template: *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate (required)\n41: │   │   ├── labels: map[string]string (optional)\n42: │   │   ├── annotations: map[string]string (optional)\n43: │   │   ├── runtimeClassName: *string (optional)\n44: │   │   ├── image: string (optional)\n45: │   │   ├── imagePullPolicy: corev1.PullPolicy (optional)\n46: │   │   ├── imagePullSecrets: []corev1.LocalObjectReference (optional)\n47: │   │   ├── environment: []corev1.EnvVar (optional)\n48: │   │   ├── command: []string (optional)\n49: │   │   ├── args: []string (optional)\n50: │   │   └── resources: corev1.ResourceRequirements (optional)\n51: │   ├── sessionTimeout: *metav1.Duration (optional)\n52: │   ├── maxSessionDuration: *metav1.Duration (optional)\n53: │   ├── warmPoolSize: *int32 (optional) — CodeInterpreter 独有\n54: │   └── authMode: AuthModeType (optional, enum: picod|none) — CodeInterpreter 独有\n55: └── Status: CodeInterpreterStatus\n56:     ├── conditions: []metav1.Condition (optional)\n57:     └── ready: bool (optional) — CodeInterpreter 独有\n58: ```\n59: \n60: ## 与 AgentRuntime 的差异\n61: \n62: | 维度 | AgentRuntime | CodeInterpreter |\n63: |------|-------------|-----------------|\n64: | 沙箱模板 | `SandboxTemplate` 嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec` | `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` 扁平化字段（image、command、args、resources 等） |\n65: | 预热池 | 无 | `WarmPoolSize *int32` |\n66: | 认证模式 | 无 | `AuthMode AuthModeType`（picod / none） |\n67: | Status | 仅 `Conditions` | `Conditions` + `Ready bool` |\n68: | 端口字段名 | `targetPort` | `ports` |\n69: \n70: ## 影响分析\n71: \n72: ### 直接影响\n73: | 组件 | 影响 | 说明 |\n74: |------|------|------|\n75: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go` | 已存在 | 类型定义文件 |\n76: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go` | 已存在 | `CodeInterpreterKind`、`CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind` 等常量 |\n77: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/zz_generated.deepcopy.go` | 已存在 | DeepCopy 方法（controller-gen 生成） |\n78: | `go.mod` | 无变更 | 依赖已在 AR-001 中引入 |\n79: \n80: ### 下游依赖（本变更完成后解锁）\n81: | 组件 | 依赖关系 |\n82: |------|----------|\n83: | `client-go/` | `make gen-client` 读取本变更的类型定义生成 CodeInterpreter Typed Client、Informer、Lister（已在 deployment/client-go.md 中确认） |\n84: | CRD YAML | `make gen-crd` 从 kubebuilder 标记生成 `config/crd/bases/` 下的 CodeInterpreter YAML |\n85: | CodeInterpreter Controller | 通过 Informer/Lister 消费 CodeInterpreter 资源，解析 SandboxTemplate 创建沙箱，管理 WarmPool |\n86: | CLI/SDK | 通过 client-go 生成的代码与 CodeInterpreter CR 交互 |\n87: | Helm Chart | 部署时安装生成的 CodeInterpreter CRD YAML |\n88: \n89: ### 无影响的组件\n90: - Router（session-routing）— 不直接依赖 CRD 类型\n91: - Session Store（Redis/Valkey）— 存储层独立\n92: - Agentd（idle cleanup）— 通过 store 接口交互\n93: - PicoD（code execution）— 沙箱内组件，与 CRD 定义无关\n94: \n95: ## 备选方案\n96: \n97: ### 方案 A：在 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 中定义（已选）\n98: **优点**：与 AR-001 AgentRuntime 共享同一 API Group 和 Version，复用 `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType` 等公共类型；与 `make gen-client` 和 `controller-gen` 工具链无缝集成；client-go 代码已在 `runtime/v1alpha1` 下为 CodeInterpreter 生成（`codeinterpreter.go`、`fake_codeinterpreter.go`、`codeinterpreter.go` informer/lister）。\n99: **缺点**：无显著缺点。\n100: \n101: ### 方案 B：将 CodeInterpreter 放在独立的 API Group（如 `codeinterpreter.agentcube.volcano.sh`）\n102: **优点**：API 边界更清晰，可独立版本化。\n103: **缺点**：无法复用 `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType` 等公共类型；client-go 代码生成器需要额外的 Group 配置；与项目中已有的 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` 下 CodeInterpreter 的 client-go 代码不一致。**否决**。\n104: \n105: ### 方案 C：与 AgentRuntime 合并为同一 CRD，通过 spec 字段区分类型\n106: **优点**：减少 CRD 数量，统一的控制器逻辑。\n107: **缺点**：AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter 的沙箱模板结构差异显著（PodSpec 嵌入 vs 扁平化字段）；CodeInterpreter 独有的 WarmPool、AuthMode 等字段对 AgentRuntime 无意义；违反单一职责原则，增加 API 复杂度。**否决**。\n108: \n109: ### 方案 D：使用 Protocol Buffers 定义 API 类型\n110: **优点**：语言无关；gRPC 原生支持。\n111: **缺点**：Kubernetes CRD 生态基于 Go struct + kubebuilder 标记；需要额外的 proto-to-CRD 转换工具链；与现有 agent-sandbox 项目的 `corev1.PodSpec` 嵌入模式不兼容。**否决**。\n112: \n113: ## 验收标准\n114: 1. `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n115: 2. `make generate` 成功生成 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 且 `git diff --exit-code` 通过\n116: 3. `CodeInterpreter` 类型的 GroupVersionKind 为 `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1, Kind=CodeInterpreter`\n117: 4. GVR resource 名称为 `codeinterpreters`\n118: 5. `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate` 不嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`，使用扁平化字段\n119: 6. `AuthMode` 枚举值为 `picod` 和 `none`\n120: 7. Status subresource 已启用（`+kubebuilder:subresource:status`）\n121: 8. `kubectl get codeinterpreters` 输出包含 `Age` 列\n122: 9. `CodeInterpreter` 与 `AgentRuntime` 共享 `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType` 类型\n123: 10. 单元测试通过（`codeinterpreter_types_test.go`）\n124: \n125: ## 状态\n126: - [ ] 提案审查\n127: - [ ] 实现\n128: - [ ] 验证\n\n(End of file - total 128 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-002: CRD CodeInterpreter 类型定义\n\n## 概述\n为 CodeInterpreter Custom Resource Definition 创建 Go 类型定义，与 AR-001 共享 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 包中的公共类型（`TargetPort`、`ProtocolType`）。\n\n## 元信息\n- **Module**: pkg/apis\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: S\n\n## 目的\nCodeInterpreter CRD 是 AgentCube 沙箱编排系统中用于声明式管理代码执行沙箱的自定义资源。与 AgentRuntime（面向通用 AI Agent 沙箱）不同，CodeInterpreter 专注于代码解释器场景，提供了更细粒度的沙箱模板控制（镜像、命令、参数、资源等扁平化字段）、预热池大小配置（`WarmPoolSize`）和认证模式（`AuthMode`：`picod` 或 `none`）。本变更将在已有的 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 包中创建完整的 Go 类型定义，为 client-go 代码生成、控制器实现和 CLI/SDK 提供类型基础。\n\n## 范围\n\n### 包含\n1. **类型定义** — `CodeInterpreter`、`CodeInterpreterSpec`、`CodeInterpreterStatus`、`CodeInterpreterList`\n2. **嵌套类型** — `CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate`（扁平化沙箱配置，不嵌入 `corev1.PodSpec`）、`AuthModeType` 枚举\n3. **共享类型复用** — `TargetPort`、`ProtocolType`（与 AR-001 AgentRuntime 共用）\n4. **Kubebuilder 标记** — `+genclient`、`+kubebuilder:subresource:status`、`+kubebuilder:printcolumn`、`+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced`","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-002/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775809890539,"end":1775809890547}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775809892698,"sessionID":"ses_2897d33c5ffeqQ82qCou8llhnY","part":{"id":"prt_d76848970001d8i3tlJlCNERW6","messageID":"msg_d76846f8b001iQpoMKvjIsfK8V","sessionID":"ses_2897d33c5ffeqQ82qCou8llhnY","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_7e9ebb7c15e1489b99fe28c8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-001/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001 任务清单\n2: \n3: > **Stage**: ST-4 (Implementation)\n4: > **Module**: `pkg/apis`\n5: > **Language**: Go\n6: > **Size**: S\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## T-001: 创建 pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 目录结构\n11: \n12: - [ ] T-001.01 创建目录 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n13: - [ ] T-001.02 确认 `go.mod` 中 `k8s.io/api`、`k8s.io/apimachinery`、`sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime` 依赖版本正确（v0.34.1 / v0.22.2）\n14: \n15: **验收**: 目录存在；`go mod tidy` 无报错\n16: \n17: ---\n18: \n19: ## T-002: 创建 doc.go — 包声明与代码生成标记\n20: \n21: - [ ] T-002.01 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go`\n22: - [ ] T-002.02 包含 `// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` 标记\n23: - [ ] T-002.03 包含 `// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh` 标记\n24: - [ ] T-002.04 包名为 `v1alpha1`\n25: \n26: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过\n27: \n28: ---\n29: \n30: ## T-003: 创建 groupversion_info.go — GroupVersion 与 SchemeBuilder\n31: \n32: - [ ] T-003.01 定义 `GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\"}`\n33: - [ ] T-003.02 定义 `SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}`\n34: - [ ] T-003.03 定义 `AddToScheme = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme`\n35: - [ ] T-003.04 导入 `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema`\n36: - [ ] T-003.05 导入 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/scheme`\n37: \n38: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；`GroupVersion.Group == \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"`；`GroupVersion.Version == \"v1alpha1\"`\n39: \n40: ---\n41: \n42: ## T-004: 创建 register.go — Kind 元数据与 Resource 辅助函数\n43: \n44: - [ ] T-004.01 定义 `AgentRuntimeKind = \"AgentRuntime\"`\n45: - [ ] T-004.02 定义 `AgentRuntimeListKind = \"AgentRuntimeList\"`\n46: - [ ] T-004.03 定义 `AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")`\n47: - [ ] T-004.04 定义 `SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion`（别名，兼容 client-go 代码生成）\n48: - [ ] T-004.05 定义 `func Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource` 返回 `GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)`\n49: - [ ] T-004.06 定义 CodeInterpreter Kind 元数据（`CodeInterpreterKind`、`CodeInterpreterGroupKind`、`CodeInterpreterListKind`、`CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind`）供后续 AR-002 使用\n50: \n51: **验收**: `Resource(\"agentruntimes\")` 返回 `{Group: \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\", Version: \"v1alpha1\", Resource: \"agentruntimes\"}`\n52: \n53: ---\n54: \n55: ## T-005: 创建 codeinterpreter_types.go — 共享类型定义\n56: \n57: - [ ] T-005.01 定义 `type ProtocolType string`\n58: - [ ] T-005.02 定义常量 `ProtocolTypeHTTP ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"` 和 `ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"`\n59: - [ ] T-005.03 定义 `type TargetPort struct`，字段：`PathPrefix string`、`Name string`、`Port uint32`、`Protocol ProtocolType`（带 `+kubebuilder:default=HTTP` 和 `+kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS` 标记）\n60: - [ ] T-005.04 定义 `type AuthModeType string`\n61: - [ ] T-005.05 定义常量 `AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"` 和 `AuthModeNone AuthModeType = \"none\"`\n62: - [ ] T-005.06 所有字段使用正确的 JSON tag（camelCase: `pathPrefix`, `name`, `port`, `protocol`）\n63: \n64: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；`ProtocolTypeHTTP == \"HTTP\"`；`TargetPort` 结构体字段与 JSON tag 映射正确\n65: \n66: ---\n67: \n68: ## T-006: 创建 agent_type.go — AgentRuntime 核心类型定义\n69: \n70: ### T-006.1: AgentRuntime 根类型\n71: \n72: - [ ] T-006.1.01 定义 `type AgentRuntime struct`，嵌入 `metav1.TypeMeta` 和 `metav1.ObjectMeta`\n73: - [ ] T-006.1.02 字段 `Spec AgentRuntimeSpec`（JSON tag: `spec`）\n74: - [ ] T-006.1.03 字段 `Status AgentRuntimeStatus`（JSON tag: `status,omitempty`）\n75: - [ ] T-006.1.04 添加标记 `+genclient`\n76: - [ ] T-006.1.05 添加标记 `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n77: - [ ] T-006.1.06 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n78: - [ ] T-006.1.07 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:subresource:status`\n79: - [ ] T-006.1.08 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced,plural=agentruntimes`\n80: - [ ] T-006.1.09 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"`\n81: \n82: ### T-006.2: AgentRuntimeSpec\n83: \n84: - [ ] T-006.2.01 定义 `type AgentRuntimeSpec struct`\n85: - [ ] T-006.2.02 字段 `Ports []TargetPort`（JSON tag: `targetPort,omitempty`）\n86: - [ ] T-006.2.03 字段 `Template *SandboxTemplate`（JSON tag: `podTemplate`，带 `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` 标记）\n87: - [ ] T-006.2.04 字段 `SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration`（JSON tag: `sessionTimeout,omitempty`，带 `+kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"` 标记）\n88: - [ ] T-006.2.05 字段 `MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration`（JSON tag: `maxSessionDuration,omitempty`，带 `+kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"` 标记）\n89: \n90: ### T-006.3: SandboxTemplate\n91: \n92: - [ ] T-006.3.01 定义 `type SandboxTemplate struct`\n93: - [ ] T-006.3.02 字段 `Labels map[string]string`（JSON tag: `labels,omitempty`）\n94: - [ ] T-006.3.03 字段 `Annotations map[string]string`（JSON tag: `annotations,omitempty`）\n95: - [ ] T-006.3.04 字段 `Spec corev1.PodSpec`（JSON tag: `spec`，带 `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` 标记）\n96: - [ ] T-006.3.05 导入 `corev1 \"k8s.io/api/core/v1\"`\n97: \n98: ### T-006.4: AgentRuntimeStatus\n99: \n100: - [ ] T-006.4.01 定义 `type AgentRuntimeStatus struct`\n101: - [ ] T-006.4.02 字段 `Conditions []metav1.Condition`（JSON tag: `conditions,omitempty`，带 `+optional` 标记）\n102: \n103: ### T-006.5: AgentRuntimeList\n104: \n105: - [ ] T-006.5.01 定义 `type AgentRuntimeList struct`，嵌入 `metav1.TypeMeta` 和 `metav1.ListMeta`\n106: - [ ] T-006.5.02 字段 `Items []AgentRuntime`（JSON tag: `items`）\n107: - [ ] T-006.5.03 添加标记 `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object`\n108: - [ ] T-006.5.04 添加标记 `+kubebuilder:object:root=true`\n109: \n110: **验收**: `go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；所有 kubebuilder 标记存在；GVK = `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1, Kind=AgentRuntime`\n111: \n112: ---\n113: \n114: ## T-007: 创建 Scheme 注册 init() 函数\n115: \n116: - [ ] T-007.01 在 `agent_type.go` 或独立文件中添加 `func init()` 调用 `SchemeBuilder.Register(&AgentRuntime{}, &AgentRuntimeList{})`\n117: \n118: **验收**: `v1alpha1.AddToScheme(scheme)` 成功将 `AgentRuntime` 和 `AgentRuntimeList` 注册到 `runtime.Scheme`\n119: \n120: ---\n121: \n122: ## T-008: 生成 DeepCopy 方法\n123: \n124: - [ ] T-008.01 运行 `make generate`（或 `controller-gen object paths=\"./pkg/apis/...\" output:dir=./pkg/apis`）\n125: - [ ] T-008.02 验证 `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 已生成在 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` 下\n126: - [ ] T-008.03 验证生成的 DeepCopy 方法覆盖 `AgentRuntime`、`AgentRuntimeSpec`、`AgentRuntimeStatus`、`AgentRuntimeList`、`SandboxTemplate`、`TargetPort`\n127: \n128: **验收**: `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` 存在；`go build ./pkg/apis/...` 编译通过；`git diff --exit-code` 通过（生成文件无意外变更）\n129: \n130: ---\n131: \n132: ## T-009: 编写单元测试 — Scheme 注册测试\n133: \n134: - [ ] T-009.01 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/groupversion_info_test.go`\n135: - [ ] T-009.02 测试 `AddToScheme(scheme)` 无错误\n136: - [ ] T-009.03 测试 `scheme.New(GVK)` 可识别 `AgentRuntime` 类型\n137: - [ ] T-009.04 测试 `scheme.New(GVKList)` 可识别 `AgentRuntimeList` 类型\n138: \n139: **验收**: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -run TestSchemeRegistration -v` 通过\n140: \n141: ---\n142: \n143: ## T-010: 编写单元测试 — GVK/GVR 常量测试\n144: \n145: - [ ] T-010.01 创建 `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register_test.go`\n146: - [ ] T-010.02 测试 `GroupVersion.Group == \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"`\n147: - [ ] T-010.03 测试 `GroupVersion.Version == \"v1alpha1\"`\n148: - [ ] T-010.04 测试 `AgentRuntimeKind == \"AgentRuntime\"`\n149: - [ ] T-010.05 测试 `AgentRuntimeListKind == \"AgentRuntimeList\"`\n150: - [ ] T-010.06 测试 `Resource(\"agentruntimes\")` 返回正